docs.text: jim mcallister ( matthew broderick ) is the type of teacher that makes american high schools proud .

docs.label: positive

docs.label: positive

docs.text: tracy flick ( reese witherspoon ) is an intelligent , outgoing , and , to quote the film , " super nice " young girl .

docs.text: she is involved in numerous extracurricular activities , always has her hand up first in class , and is extremely popular among most of the student body .
